snippet.title: Winkeltje Early Access
snippet.description:
Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/949290/Winkeltje/

Winkeltje is a game about building, decorating and running a small shop in the days of old. Deal with the day-to-day business as the owner of your very own store.

Join the community on Discord: https://discord.gg/ZSMEenk
